&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>나의 경우 R(4.0.5), Biomart(2.46.3)을 사용해주었다. 참고로 R(&amp;gt;=2.1) 버전을 필요로 한다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Differential gene expression analysis using edgeR</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/transcriptomics/transcriptomics-edger/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/transcriptomics/transcriptomics-edger/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="differential-gene-expression-analysis-using-edger">
 Differential gene expression analysis using edgeR
